{"type":"message","id":"37f57286","parentId":"ab1cfcee","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:29:37.461Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The MCP works fine - it just needs the amzSite parameter. This is a different issue from what the user reported as \"天天失败\". Let me look at what might have been going wrong previously. The key issue is that `get_time` always worked (because it's one of the few that didn't need auth), but most other calls failed due to truncated key.\n\nNow the key is actually working. Let me test a more realistic product search to verify, then do a proper product search and write results to the bitable.\n\nThe user's complaint is that selection has been failing for many days with no data. Let me investigate the Shopee category data - since the user seems to want TikTok-related data, but the available tools seem to be mostly for Amazon, Shopee, Temu, Walmart.\n\nFor TikTok product trend data, the user needs to provide a productId. I don't have product IDs offhand.\n\nLet me test the system properly and see if it's actually working now. I'll do a quick test call and then start doing actual product searches.\n\nThe key problem seems to be:\n1. The mcporter config had a truncated key (Bearer rhblyi…qt09 instead of the full key)\n2. This caused authentication failures for most API calls\n3. get_time, category_name_search, similar_product_feature worked because they apparently don't check auth\n\nNow the key is being read correctly from /tmp/sorftime_key.txt approach, but actually looking at the mcporter config, the key is showing as truncated too. But it seems to work through mcporter...\n\nLet me just test if a real search works and proceed with doing actual product selection work.\n","thinkingSignature":"2d93bfe5210fde7bd64b7d71224ba400ec329606b5fd292a99630fd6ddc32754"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jqwv038mrz7r_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call \"sorftime-mcp.potential_product(searchName: \\\"tiktok viral product\\\", amzSite: \\\"US\\\", page: 1)\" --config /home/halei/workspace-tts/config/mcporter.json 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":124,"output":416,"cacheRead":59840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60380,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780453762856,"responseId":"066ec489e37e32a058b46821036a26fb"}}
