{"type":"message","id":"d91f300f","parentId":"00e39f07","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:32:06.643Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I now have real data. The issue is that the cron jobs have been failing due to \"AI service temporarily overloaded\". But the MCP connection is working fine.\n\nLet me now execute the actual selection workflow right now to get products into the Feishu bitable. The user is frustrated - I should just do it now instead of explaining.\n\nLet me analyze the data I already have from the Hair Claws category report, filtering by the entry window criteria:\n- 上架时间 ≤30天: filter for products with 上架日期 around 2026-05-04 to 2026-06-02\n- 近7天销量增长率 ≥50%: can't check directly, need to look at monthly sales\n\n\n- 总销量 100-500单: filter for 月销量 in range 100-500\n- 评价数 50-200条: filter for 评论数 in range 50-200\n- 同款卖家数量 ≤20个: can't check directly\n- 客单价 3-10美元: filter for 价格 in range 3-10\n- 退货率 ≤10%: can't check\n\nLooking at the Top100 data, most products are way too established with massive sales volumes and review counts. I need to find products that fit the entry window - recently launched with modest but growing traction.\n\nScanning through the results, B0FQPKX93K is educational and outside the hair accessories niche. B0F636T849 shows 6846 monthly sales but was launched in May 2025, so it's nearly a year old - that's too long in the market. Most other candidates like B0FLDSWRCD and B0FX4KCGDK are also either too old or have sales volumes that don't match what I'm looking for.\n\nI'm not seeing products in that 100-500 monthly sales range, which suggests the Hair Claws category might be oversaturated. Let me try a different approach - searching with tighter filters like a price range of $3-10 and monthly volume between 100-500 to find items that are newer to the market.\n","thinkingSignature":"51d8c044815cb7ea65e11581ac1267605f81fc7b196595328acef9be21ac4589"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_trr0eq7zjw3d_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call \"sorftime-mcp.potential_product(amzSite: \\\"US\\\", price_min: 3, price_max: 10, month_sales_volume_min: 100, month_sales_volume_max: 500, page: 1)\" --config /home/halei/workspace-tts/config/mcporter.json 2>&1 | head -80"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6410,"output":525,"cacheRead":67392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74327,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780453913953,"responseId":"066ec51a75049c0ecd064d5189d4651c"}}
