{"type":"message","id":"90fe1bc5","parentId":"b2268f5b","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:33:29.402Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the API is working. Now let me do a proper product search for the hair accessories niche with the correct criteria matching the SOP entry time window filters.\n\nLet me now run the actual product search. I need to apply the SOP entry time window filters:\n- 上架时间 ≤30天\n- 近7天销量增长率 ≥50%\n- 总销量 100-500单\n- 评价数 50-200条\n- 同款卖家数量 ≤20个\n- 客单价 3-10美元\n- 退货率 ≤10%\n\nThe `potential_product` doesn't give me all these fields. I should use `shopee_product_search` or `temu_product_search` for TK data. But the user is doing Amazon hair accessories data for TikTok.\n\nActually, looking at the SOP - it's about doing Amazon category reports and then selecting products. \n\nNow I'll execute the full selection process manually and write the results to the Feishu bitable.\n","thinkingSignature":"549b4981a3398e32eefbab8c551b10b1e678185d7a3d88718160dfb470b46f2f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_58y5jit7ueze_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Get Hair Claws category report for the past 2 weeks to find recent entrants\nmcporter call \"sorftime-mcp.category_report_from_history(startDate: \\\"2026-05-20\\\", endDate: \\\"2026-06-02\\\", nodeId: \\\"23623510011\\\", amzSite: \\\"US\\\")\" --config /home/halei/workspace-tts/config/mcporter.json 2>&1 | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\ndata = json.load(sys.stdin)\nproducts = data.get('Top100产品', [])\ntoday = '2026-06-03'\n\ndef days_from(date_str):\n    from datetime import datetime\n    try:\n        d = datetime.strptime(date_str, '%Y-%m-%d')\n        delta = (datetime(2026,6,3) - d).days\n        return delta\n    except:\n        return 999\n\nprint('Total products:', len(products))\nprint()\nprint('=== 入场时间窗口过滤 (≤30天上架) ===')\npassed = []\nfor p in products:\n    days = days_from(p.get('上架日期',''))\n    price = float(p.get('价格',0))\n    reviews = int(p.get('评论数',0) or 0)\n    monthly = int(p.get('月销量','0') or 0)\n    \n    # Skip if no reviews or very few\n    if reviews < 10:\n        continue\n    \n    if days <= 30 and 3 <= price <= 10 and 50 <= reviews <= 500 and monthly >= 100 and monthly <= 500:\n        passed.append(p)\n\nprint(f'通过入场窗口产品: {len(passed)}')\nprint()\nfor i, p in enumerate(passed[:10]):\n    print(f\\\"{i+1}. {p['标题'][:50]}...\\\")\n    print(f\\\"   ASIN: {p['ASIN']} | 上架:{p['上架日期']}({days_from(p['上架日期'])}天) | 月销:{p['月销量']} | 价格:\\${p['价格']} | 评价:{p['评论数']} | 星级:{p['星级']}\\\")\n\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":602,"output":688,"cacheRead":76544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77834,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780453999900,"responseId":"066ec57048a9db698fcdb3549f62a473"}}
