{"type":"message","id":"5750e617","parentId":"9c2d1bc1","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:35:09.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I have 20 products from TikTok. Let me try to find ones that might be in the Amazon Hair Claws category by checking the tiktok_product_detail for some of the top ones. But the issue is that TikTok Product IDs and Amazon ASINs are different systems.\n\nActually, let me think about what the user is really asking. They say the daily cron job has been failing continuously (mostly due to AI service overload). I already confirmed:\n1. The API key is working (get_time works)\n2. The problem was the cron runs were hitting AI service overload\n\nThe user says \"好多天选品不成功，并且没有数据\" - meaning many days of failed selection and no data.\n\n\nThe cron jobs are failing due to AI service timeouts, so I'll bypass that and manually run the selection process myself. I can leverage the API to find viable hair accessory products in the US market, filter by price and sales volume, then write the results to the spreadsheet.\n","thinkingSignature":"824ad20649882bd13e0778fce46217f581c09e2d897c9d4e4786389638b0dfd6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4apslbpk67zs_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Try to get tiktok products that might overlap with Amazon hair claws category\n# and look for newer entrants with lower prices\n\npython3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('/tmp/tiktok_hair.json') as f:\n    content = f.read().strip()\n    \ndata = json.loads(content)\nproducts = data if isinstance(data, list) else []\n\nprint(f'Total TikTok products: {len(products)}')\nprint()\n\n# Filter by: price 3-10, monthly销量 100-5000\nfiltered = []\nfor p in products:\n    price = float(p.get('价格', 0))\n    monthly = int(p.get('月销量', 0) or 0)\n    weekly = int(p.get('周销量', 0) or 0)\n    \n    if 3 <= price <= 10 and monthly >= 50 and monthly <= 5000:\n        filtered.append(p)\n\nprint(f'价格3-10美元, 月销50+的产品: {len(filtered)}')\nprint()\n\n# Sort by monthly volume\nfiltered.sort(key=lambda x: int(x.get('月销量','0') or 0), reverse=True)\n\nfor i, p in enumerate(filtered[:15]):\n    print(f\\\"{i+1}. {p['标题'][:50]}\\\")\n    print(f\\\"   ProductId: {p['ProductId']} | 月销:{p['月销量']} | 周销:{p['周销量']} | 价格:\\${p['价格']} | 卖家:{p.get('卖家','')}\\\")\n\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":760,"output":551,"cacheRead":80384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81695,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780454097317,"responseId":"066ec5d1a24254310929ff2727bd9909"}}
