{"type":"message","id":"53c9ea93","parentId":"236641f2","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:35:49.081Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me try to use the search capability more directly to find hair clips specific products on Shopee. But the API returns general products, not specifically hair clips.\n\nActually, let me take a different approach. The user's complaint is that the bot has been failing for many days. I need to:\n1. Fix the key config (already done)\n2. Do a manual product selection run now \n3. Write to Feishu bitable\n4. Also fix the cron job's \"overloaded\" error\n\nBut the cron error \"The AI service is temporarily overloaded\" suggests MiniMax API issues. I should check if there's a fallback model configured or if we need to add retries.\n\n\nNow I'll execute a comprehensive product search across Shopee, TikTok, and Amazon for hair clips and accessories, then screen them against the entry window criteria and document the results in Feishu.\n","thinkingSignature":"244f0020ecccf247272aaff43c73b7ca3dba6bdfcd6c51ed71993dc9b797e9f1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_a2951at12yc4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nwith open('/tmp/shopee_my.json') as f:\n    data = json.load(f)\n\nproducts = data.get('Products', [])\nprint(f'Total products returned: {len(products)}')\n\ndef parse_date(date_str):\n    try:\n        return datetime.strptime(date_str, '%Y-%m-%d')\n    except:\n        return None\n\ntoday = datetime(2026, 6, 3)\n\n# Filter: price 3-10, monthly 100-500, 上架30天内\n# Note: Shopee doesn't have 上架日期 directly but has SaleTime\npassed = []\nfor p in products:\n    price = float(p.get('Price', 0))\n    monthly = int(p.get('SalesCount', 0) or 0)\n    sale_time = p.get('SaleTime', '')\n    ratings = int(p.get('RatingsCount', 0) or 0)\n    \n    if not (3 <= price <= 10 and 100 <= monthly <= 500):\n        continue\n    \n    if sale_time:\n        d = parse_date(sale_time)\n        if d:\n            days = (today - d).days\n            if days <= 30 and ratings >= 50:\n                passed.append({**p, 'days_ago': days})\n\nprint(f'\\n通过入场窗口(3-10美元,月销100-500,30天内,50+评价): {len(passed)}')\nfor i, p in enumerate(passed[:10]):\n    print(f\"{i+1}. {p['Title'][:50]}\")\n    print(f\"   ID:{p['ProductId']} | 上架:{p['SaleTime']}({p['days_ago']}天) | 月销:{p['SalesCount']} | 价:${p['Price']} | 评价:{p['RatingsCount']}\")\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":182,"output":603,"cacheRead":82240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83025,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780454134133,"responseId":"066ec5f6b17056bf7a081be7bba69956"}}
