{"type":"message","id":"017db168","parentId":"abb8e0bb","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:36:57.199Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is that Hair Claws (node 23623510011) is a very mature category with no new entrants in the last 30 days. The top products are mostly from 2021-2025.\n\nThe problem is the SOP is designed for finding \"刚启动爆发的品\" but Hair Claws category is already saturated with no recent newcomers.\n\nLet me check the other potential issue - maybe the cron job itself isn't working properly due to the AI service failures. The cron runs at 9AM every day and has been failing with \"AI service temporarily overloaded\".\n\nLet me just directly run a selection and write results, then explain the situation clearly to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"f38c00c4bdafbe799fa62716c20c63645f15fddce8380b8a7bab3c12cf22300a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2e7pr5y132tc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Let's get the category report for Hair Claws in the past 14 days to see 30-day data\nmcporter call \"sorftime-mcp.category_report_from_history(startDate: \\\"2026-05-20\\\", endDate: \\\"2026-06-02\\\", nodeId: \\\"23623510011\\\", amzSite: \\\"US\\\")\" --config /home/halei/workspace-tts/config/mcporter.json 2>&1 | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\ndata = json.load(sys.stdin)\nproducts = data.get('Top100产品', [])\nstats = data.get('类目统计报告', {})\n\nprint('=== Hair Claws 类目报告 (2026-05-20 ~ 2026-06-02) ===')\nprint(f'类目: {stats.get(\\\"类目名称\\\",\\\"\\\")}')\nprint(f'Top100月销量: {stats.get(\\\"top100产品月销量\\\",\\\"\\\")}')\nprint(f'Top100月销额: \\${stats.get(\\\"top100产品月销额\\\",\\\"\\\")}')\nprint(f'平均价格: \\${float(stats.get(\\\"average_price\\\",0)):.2f}')\nprint(f'中位价格: \\${float(stats.get(\\\"median_price\\\",0)):.2f}')\nprint(f'Top3品牌占比: {stats.get(\\\"top3_brands_sales_volume_share\\\",\\\"\\\")}')\nprint(f'亚马逊自营占比: {stats.get(\\\"amazonOwned_sales_volume_share\\\",\\\"\\\")}')\nprint()\nprint(f'Top100产品总数: {len(products)}')\n\nfrom datetime import datetime\ntoday = datetime(2026,6,3)\n\n# Count products by age\nnew_count = sum(1 for p in products if (today - datetime.strptime(p.get('上架日期','2000-01-01'), '%Y-%m-%d')).days <= 30)\nprint(f'30天内新品: {new_count}')\nprint(f'30-90天: {sum(1 for p in products if 30 < (today - datetime.strptime(p.get(\\\"上架日期\\\",\\\"2000-01-01\\\"), \\\"%Y-%m-%d\\\")).days <= 90)}')\nprint(f'90天以上: {sum(1 for p in products if (today - datetime.strptime(p.get(\\\"上架日期\\\",\\\"2000-01-01\\\"), \\\"%Y-%m-%d\\\")).days > 90)}')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3843,"output":678,"cacheRead":83456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87977,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780454209514,"responseId":"066ec64242ba13047d35a2e797097f81"}}
