{"type":"message","id":"25d1fa9c","parentId":"29b196de","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:37:39.071Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me just focus on answering the user. They said the agent has been failing every day and there is no data. The cron job runs daily at 9AM but has been failing with AI service errors. The MCP key was truncated but is now fixed.\n\nLet me explain the situation and what I found. The main issue seems to be:\n1. MCP key was truncated in the config (fixed now)\n2. AI service was overloaded causing cron failures\n3. Hair Claws category is very saturated with long-standing products (no 30-day entrants in Top100)\n\nI should tell the user what I found, what the issues were, and what we can do. Let me be honest about the situation and suggest improvements.\n","thinkingSignature":"c45aad28b277f5b3b1c0091d63fcdcf2d46eee224011f3c61bfc998210ebb792"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n问题分析完了，给你汇报一下情况：\n\n**发现的问题：**\n\n1. **MCP Key 配置截断** — 配置文件里存的 key 是截断版（`Bearer…qt09`），但奇怪的是 mcporter CLI 调用竟然还能用。刚刚已修复为完整 key。\n\n2. **AI 服务过载** — cron 任务最近连续 10 多次都报 `AI service is temporarily overloaded`，这是导致每天选品跑失败的主要原因，不是代码问题，是 MiniMax API 临时过载。\n\n3. **Hair Claws 类目饱和** — 从 Amazon Hair Claws（NodeId: 23623510011）Top100 数据来看，**近30天内上架的新品数为 0**，所有爆款都是老品（2021-2022年上架）。这就是为什么按 SOP 选不出品——入场窗口压根没有产品能过筛。\n\n**根本原因：** Hair Claws 这个品类已经是红海中的红海，Kitsch、Sisiaipu、SMKSL 三个品牌吃掉了 41% 的销量，Top100 里 89 个产品都是 365 天以上的老品。跟品策略在这个节点已经没什么红利了。\n\n**建议调整方向：**\n\n我建议两个选项，你来决定：\n\n**A. 换细分赛道** — Hair Claws 下还有更细的子分类，比如 `RF`、`Camisoles` 等，有些新品占比更高（5-14%），或许还有入场空间。\n\n**B. 放宽入场时间窗口** — 从 30 天放宽到 60-90 天，牺牲一些\"新鲜度\"换取引入更多产品。\n\n**C. 暂停每日自动选品** — AI 过载问题不是我这边能解决的，等 MiniMax 稳定后再恢复。\n\n你想怎么处理？我可以现在就跑一轮能用的选品（放宽参数），或者等你决定方向后再调整。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":13926,"output":529,"cacheRead":75008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89463,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780454249101,"responseId":"066ec6699bb7ab25cbe819c4f3332083"}}
