{"type":"message","id":"d810f31f","parentId":"a79ef0a2","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:43:19.868Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is sharing a new SOP for TikTok/Shopee hair accessories product selection. This is a completely different SOP from the previous one (v5.2). This new SOP focuses on:\n\n1. **Phase 1**: TikTok trending products - scan every 2 hours, looking for hair accessories that meet specific criteria\n2. **Phase 2**: Shopee platform validation - verify on Shopee Vietnam + Thailand\n3. **Phase 3**: 1688 supply chain and profit calculation\n\nThe user wants me to look at this new SOP. Let me acknowledge it and note the key differences from the old SOP.\n\nKey things I notice about this new SOP:\n1. It's specifically for TikTok hair accessories (越南+泰国)\n2. It's a 3-phase funnel system (TikTok → Shopee → 1688)\n3. It uses different tools: tiktok_product_trend, shopee_product_search, 1688_supplier_search\n4. It's more aggressive - looking for \"黑马\" (dark horse) products, not just following established best sellers\n5. It has a completely different criteria set - focuses on 24-hour growth rate, video count, etc.\n6. It has a S-level emergency detection for products that double sales in 12 hours\n7. Daily budget is 1000 MCP calls out of 30000 total\n\nThe user is probably asking me to update my workflow to match this new SOP. Let me acknowledge and ask what they want me to do with it.\n","thinkingSignature":"bdb905ae0dc7fd6d895dc4e27b43a5197dd06179513ae71fd2bd1a349efc3268"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n收到新 SOP，这是完全不同的选品逻辑。\n\n**新 SOP vs 旧 SOP 核心差异：**\n\n| 维度 | 旧 SOP (v5.2) | 新 SOP |\n|------|---------------|--------|\n| **核心策略** | 跟品为主（跟亚马逊爆款） | 抓黑马（TikTok 实时爆款） |\n| **数据源** | 亚马逊 → TK 验证 | TikTok → Shopee 验证 → 1688 利润 |\n| **筛选逻辑** | 入场时间窗口（30天静态卡） | 24小时销量环比+带货视频数（动态） |\n| **紧急机制** | 无 | **S级爆款**：12小时销量翻倍+视频≥15个 |\n| **扫描频率** | 每日一次 | 每2小时轮询 |\n| **接口重点** | Amazon category_report | tiktok_product_trend + shopee_product_search |\n| **输出** | 写入多维表 | 联动妙手 ERP 自动上架 |\n\n**新 SOP 的三级漏斗：**\n\n```\n阶段1：TikTok黑马抓取 → 阶段2：Shopee生命周期验证 → 阶段3：1688利润核算 → 妙手ERP上架\n```\n\n这个 SOP 明显比之前那个激进得多，更适合 TikTok 发饰这种爆款生命周期只有3-7天的品类。\n\n**现在的问题：** 当前配置里用的是旧 SOP（`category_report_from_history` 亚马逊路线），而且 AI 过载导致 cron 任务一直失败。\n\n你想怎么推进？\n\n**A.** 把这个新 SOP 写到文件里，更新 cron 任务逻辑\n**B.** 现在手动跑一轮新 SOP 的阶段1，看看能抓到什么品\n**C.** 先修复 AI 过载问题，再切换到新 SOP"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2056,"output":681,"cacheRead":89211,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91948,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780472579049,"responseId":"066f0e03446b5bbf122ef26e557bd27d"}}
