{"type":"message","id":"a6eda492","parentId":"22442cbd","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:47:44.885Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to update the SOP and create a new Feishu document. I've done both:\n\n1. Written the new SOP to local file: `/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v6.0.md`\n2. Created a new Feishu doc: \"选品策略 6.0-越泰市场趋势黑马拦截策略\" at https://www.feishu.cn/docx/KlpcdGesGoIii9xPEZYcMa3znNd\n\nNow I should update MEMORY.md to reflect the new SOP location and key details. Also, I should update the cron job to use the new SOP logic.\n\nLet me update MEMORY.md first, then tell the user what was done and ask what to do next.\n","thinkingSignature":"dbd74169b60429772a6038524d4f69c3e4e36b0e82279349ce08819ddff66cf9"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n搞定，两个地方都更新了：\n\n**本地文件：** `/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v6.0.md`\n\n**飞书新文档：** https://www.feishu.cn/docx/KlpcdGesGoIii9xPEZYcMa3znNd\n- 文档名称：**选品策略 6.0-越泰市场趋势黑马拦截策略**\n\n---\n\n**SOP v6.0 核心变更：**\n\n| 变更点 | 内容 |\n|--------|------|\n| 数据源 | TikTok → Shopee → 1688（新三级漏斗） |\n| 筛选逻辑 | 24小时销量环比+带货视频数（动态）替代原来的30天静态入场窗口 |\n| 输出终点 | 飞书多维表格（去掉了妙手ERP） |\n| 紧急机制 | S级爆款：12小时销量翻倍+视频≥15个+星级≥4.3 |\n| 扫描频率 | 每2小时轮询（原来是每日一次） |\n\n---\n\n现在要做什么？\n\n**A.** 更新 cron 任务逻辑，按新 SOP 跑每日选品\n**B.** 现在手动跑一轮新 SOP 的阶段1，看看能抓到哪些 TikTok 黑马\n**C.** 先测试一下 MCP 接口能返回哪些字段，确保筛选标准能落地"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1377,"output":432,"cacheRead":93547,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95356,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780472852605,"responseId":"066f0f156358262bdb1557ae3d0cbb07"}}
