{"type":"message","id":"6865263f","parentId":"8bb7003c","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:48:29.587Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I need to write a cron job for the \"every 2 hours polling\" requirement. Yes, the new SOP says scan every 2 hours. The current cron runs once daily at 9AM. I need to update it to run every 2 hours for the TikTok monitoring part.\n\nLet me think about this:\n1. The new SOP requires scanning every 2 hours (12 times per day)\n2. Each scan uses up to 300 MCP calls (phase 1)\n3. The daily budget is 1000 MCP calls\n\nBut running a cron every 2 hours might be too aggressive and would consume a lot of the daily budget. Let me think about what makes sense.\n\nActually, looking at the SOP more carefully:\n- Phase 1: 300 calls per scan, scan every 2 hours = 12 * 300 = 3600 calls/day just for phase 1\n- But the budget is only 1000 calls/day\n\nThis means the every-2-hour scanning is not sustainable with the current budget. I should point this out to the user.\n\nHowever, the user asked specifically if I need to write a cron for this. Let me explain the situation and propose a practical solution.\n\nActually, let me reconsider. The \"every 2 hours\" is for active monitoring of a smaller set of products. I could:\n1. Run phase 1 every 2 hours but with a smaller batch\n2. Or run phase 1 every 2 hours but only check the top 20 products instead of 80\n3. Or use a smarter approach where the first run of the day does the full scan and subsequent runs only check for S-level emergency products\n\nLet me propose a practical compromise to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"1720b53bc6b8e6fb0a6d5b2160a617cf86926540e1f829c5d10641bb2c1eafa7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n是的，但要算一下额度够不够：\n\n**每2小时扫描的额度消耗估算：**\n- 阶段1：每次扫描约 300 次 MCP\n- 每天 12 次 × 300 = **3600 次/天**\n- 但你的每日预算只有 **1000 次**\n- 直接每2小时跑会把30天的额度在8天内用完\n\n**更现实的方案：**\n\n| 方案 | 频率 | 每日消耗 | 可持续天数 |\n|------|------|---------|----------|\n| 全量扫描 | 每2小时 | 3600次 | 8天 |\n| 精简扫描 | 每2小时（限20品） | 1200次 | 25天 |\n| **推荐：混合模式** | 白天每3小时 | 600次 | 50天 |\n\n**推荐方案：混合模式**\n- 白天（9:00-21:00）每3小时跑一次阶段1（限30品）\n- 每次检测到 S级爆款立即触发完整流程\n- 夜间降低频率，节省额度\n\n要按这个方案更新 cron 吗？还是你有别的想法（比如减少扫描频率或者优先保证额度）？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3433,"output":605,"cacheRead":91938,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95976,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780472895125,"responseId":"066f0f3f21a8336e9f379d0f8c08124c"}}
