{"type":"message","id":"0290c576","parentId":"e3bd466e","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:49:44.815Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user accepted the recommended plan and also mentioned they purchased 30,000 calls at once (one-time purchase, not monthly). This changes the math significantly - with 30,000 calls total and the recommended plan consuming about 600/day, it would last 50 days.\n\nBut wait - the user said \"一次性购买了30000次额度\" which means they bought 30,000 calls at once, not a monthly allocation. This is a one-time purchase of 30,000 calls, not a monthly budget. So the daily budget of 1000 is actually not a monthly limit - it's a self-imposed daily spending limit.\n\nWith 30,000 calls total and the recommended plan at ~600/day, it would last about 50 days. That makes sense.\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Update the cron job to implement the \"混合模式\" - every 3 hours during day time (9AM-9PM), so 5 times: 9:00, 12:00, 15:00, 18:00, 21:00\n2. Update MEMORY.md to reflect the new SOP and the 30,000 calls one-time purchase\n3. Update the cron job payload to use the new SOP logic\n\nLet me first update MEMORY.md, then update the cron job.\n\nThe cron should run at:\n- 9:00, 12:00, 15:00, 18:00, 21:00 every day (5 times)\n- This is a cron expression: 0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *\n\nActually wait - let me think about this. The SOP says every 2 hours but with 30K total calls. If we do every 3 hours 5 times per day:\n- Phase 1: 30 products × ~5 calls each = ~150 calls per run × 5 = 750/day just for phase 1\n\n\n- Plus phases 2 and 3 for items that pass phase 1\n\nSo roughly 600-800 calls per day total, which means the 30,000 calls would last around 40-50 days. Now I'll set up the cron job with the expression 0 9,12,15,18,21 * * * to run 5 times daily during waking hours, update MEMORY.md with the new SOP details, and configure the cron message/payload accordingly.\n","thinkingSignature":"58db8ee341a91968b5859efcfeec1146ef9515ed6962aceae24613b2f2fac49f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n一次性买30K，那额度很充裕，按推荐方案能跑 **40-50天**。\n\n我现在更新 cron + MEMORY：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xbcucxft62o4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\njobs = d.get('jobs', [])\nfor j in jobs:\n    if 'TK选品' in j.get('name',''):\n        print(json.dumps(j, indent=2))\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":894,"output":612,"cacheRead":95100,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96606,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780472966990,"responseId":"066f0f87b73870482fa08ff9697f2b4c"}}
