{"type":"message","id":"43a0d0ed","parentId":"309cedd4","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:50:27.307Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to update the cron job to use the new SOP v6.0 logic. The user accepted the \"混合模式\" (hybrid mode):\n- Daytime (9:00-21:00) every 3 hours run phase 1 (limited to 30 products)\n- Detect S-level emergency products and trigger full flow immediately\n- Night time reduced frequency to save quota\n\nWith 30000 quota and 1000/day, they have 30 days. But if we do 5 runs per day (9AM, 12PM, 3PM, 6PM, 9PM), each run using say 300 calls, that's 1500/day which is over budget.\n\nActually, the user said they bought 30000 calls一次性 (one-time purchase). So we have more budget flexibility.\n\nLet me plan:\n- 5 runs per day (9AM, 12PM, 3PM, 6PM, 9PM) - daytime\n- Each run: ~300 MCP calls for phase 1 (30 products)\n- Daily total: ~1500 calls (over the previously mentioned 1000/day budget)\n- With 30000 calls, this would last 20 days\n\nBut wait, the user said the daily budget was 1000 calls (30 days to use 30000). With the hybrid mode they might be OK with using more since they bought 30000一次性.\n\nLet me create the new cron jobs:\n\n1. Main selection job - every 3 hours during daytime (9, 12, 15, 18, 21)\n2. This will run phase 1 (TikTok trending) with 30 products max\n3. S-level emergency detection triggers full flow immediately\n\nActually, I think I should create ONE job that fires every 3 hours, and inside the agent logic it decides what to do based on time of day.\n\n\nI'll set up the cron with 5 triggers across the day at 9AM, noon, 3PM, 6PM, and 9PM. The job ID stays the same for the main workflow, and I just need to update the message to reflect the new v6.0 SOP. Since I'm keeping the same job ID, I don't need to remove and recreate—just patch it.\n","thinkingSignature":"0197066053ee04db7a441f7201e9cfa1819f62f5cf8a761bdfbbadfc6d28909a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，30000次一次性购买，那每天可以放开跑。我现在更新 cron 任务，用新的混合模式 + v6.0 SOP 逻辑。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_13drayjakpiy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json | python3 -c \"\nimport sys, json\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\n# Update the TK选品 job to use new v6.0 SOP with hybrid mode\njobs = d.get('jobs', [])\nfor j in jobs:\n    if j.get('id') == '5c75bbb4-b1c3-446b-bde9-74bed5a396c6':\n        j['name'] = 'TK选品-越泰黑马拦截-v6.0'\n        j['description'] = '越泰市场趋势黑马拦截策略v6.0：每3小时执行阶段1（白天9-21点），S级爆款触发全流程，直接写入飞书多维表格'\n        j['schedule'] = {\n            'kind': 'cron',\n            'expr': '0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *',\n            'tz': 'Asia/Shanghai'\n        }\n        j['payload'] = {\n            'kind': 'agentTurn',\n            'message': '''执行v6.0选品流程（越泰市场趋势黑马拦截）：\n1. 调用tiktok_product_trend扫描越南+泰国发饰品类，筛选24小时销量环比≥100%、带货视频≥8个、星级≥4.2、客单价$1.5-$8的商品（限30品）\n2. 发现S级爆款（12小时销量翻倍+视频≥15个+星级≥4.3）立即触发阶段2+3完整验证\n3. 通过的商品调用ali1688_similar_product核算采购价和毛利率（目标≥40%）\n4. 将结果写入飞书多维表格AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd/tblHU2do30jzinJT，包含：标题、主图、TikTok销量、Shopee验证数据、1688采购价、毛利率、推荐等级（S/A/B级）\n5. 发送选品报告到飞书'''\n        }\n        print('Updated job:')\n        print(json.dumps(j, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\n        break\n\n# Save\nwith open('/tmp/jobs_updated.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(d, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\nprint('\\\\nSaved to /tmp/jobs_updated.json')\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":202,"output":1020,"cacheRead":96539,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97761,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780472999919,"responseId":"066f0fa9d4aaed4e7da0f65b8e6e63e1"}}
