{"type":"message","id":"09f0eb8d","parentId":"b11a8c3c","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:50:51.214Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the cron job is updated. Now let me also update MEMORY.md to reflect the new SOP version and cron schedule. Then tell the user what's been done.\n","thinkingSignature":"ebfe89ccba5f3e81a63278f95a7bda3464a8d4d95a3555fdaacc4b6f64e094e5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lndsnihdui7i_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"## 选品核心逻辑（v6.0 越泰黑马拦截策略）\n- **核心策略：趋势黑马拦截 + 三级漏斗验证 + 1688利润终选**\n- 数据源：TikTok → Shopee → 1688 → 飞书多维表格\n- 扫描频率：白天每3小时（9、12、15、18、21点）\n- 筛选：24小时销量环比≥100%、带货视频≥8个、星级≥4.2、客单价$1.5-$8\n- S级爆款：12小时销量翻倍+视频≥15个+星级≥4.3 → 立即触发完整流程","oldText":"## 选品核心逻辑（v5.2）\n- **核心策略：跟品为主 + 套装/组合扩展**\n- 所有选品前先过「入场时间窗口」7项过滤器\n- 不符合入场时间窗口的品直接淘汰，不进入后续评分"},{"newText":"- SOP（飞书文档）: https://www.feishu.cn/docx/KlpcdGesGoIii9xPEZYcMa3znNd（选品策略 6.0-越泰市场趋势黑马拦截策略）\n- SOP（本地）: /home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v6.0.md","oldText":"- SOP（飞书文档）: https://www.feishu.cn/docx/Q9NGdkdnio7YAmx2Ok7ccHc3nbb\n- SOP（本地）: /home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP.md"},{"newText":"## Cron 任务\n- TK选品-越泰黑马拦截-v6.0：每天 9、12、15、18、21点执行\n- 30000次额度已购入（2026-06-03）","oldText":"## 待记"}],"path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":214,"output":507,"cacheRead":97725,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98446,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780473037493,"responseId":"066f0fce38d95e672a29308d3c6d6e30"}}
