{"type":"message","id":"292cfa14","parentId":"0bfbd9e7","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:51:34.707Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the existing bitable fields. The fields are already set up for the old SOP. The new v6.0 SOP has different output requirements (TikTok data, Shopee validation, etc.) that don't fully match the existing fields.\n\nHowever, I should not try to redesign the bitable structure right now - that would be a significant change. Let me just note that the existing fields can work with some mapping:\n\nFor v6.0, the output would need:\n- 商品名称 (title) ✓\n- 产品连接 (TikTok URL) - existing field \"产品连接\"\n- 1688产品主图 (1688 image) ✓\n\n\n- 售价 (price) - \"售价（本地货币）\"\n- 月销量 - existing ✓\n- 增长率 - existing ✓\n- 利润率(%) - existing ✓\n- 推荐等级 (S/A/B级) - existing ✓\n- 采集状态 - existing ✓\n\nThe main gaps are around TikTok-specific metrics like 24-hour sales trends, video content performance, Shopee ratings, and supplier pricing information. I'll need to document these limitations for now.\n","thinkingSignature":"39a530b04c55054f3b38fe9bd1405d7000cd677fcb9905f3b44d8fe8bc44ea1c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n搞定了，以下是更新汇总：\n\n---\n\n**✅ 已完成：**\n\n1. **新 SOP 文件** \n   - 本地：`/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v6.0.md`\n   - 飞书：`https://www.feishu.cn/docx/KlpcdGesGoIii9xPEZYcMa3znNd`\n\n2. **Cron 任务已更新**\n   - 名称：TK选品-越泰黑马拦截-v6.0\n   - 频率：每天 **9、12、15、18、21点** 执行（白天每3小时）\n   - 逻辑：阶段1扫描30品 → S级爆款触发完整流程 → 写入飞书多维表格 → 发报告\n\n3. **MEMORY.md 已更新**\n   - SOP v6.0 路径更新\n   - Cron 配置记录\n\n4. **30000次额度已确认**（充足）\n\n---\n\n**多维表格字段现状：**\n\n现有字段基本覆盖 v6.0 需要的核心指标：商品名称、价格、销量、增长率、利润率、推荐等级（S/A/B级）、采集状态等。但缺少一些 TikTok 特有字段（如24小时销量、新增带货视频数、达人结构）。如果需要可以后续补充。\n\n---\n\n**下一步：**\n\n要现在手动跑一轮 v6.0 阶段1测试一下吗？看看能抓到哪些 TikTok 黑马？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2549,"output":531,"cacheRead":98443,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101523,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780473073445,"responseId":"066f0ff26ccc0a7573162f8030b62851"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4751ed9f","parentId":"292cfa14","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:51:51.562Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6ec99ff7f0a8c29fad4858f86a1\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-06-03 15:51 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n看一下这个建议有必要修改吗|\n**关于 ****shopee_product_search**** 的平替**： 在阶段2中，你写到了批量调用 shopee_product_search。Sorftime 的 MCP 服务中，对于各大平台的查询逻辑，通常是先通过**类目报告**（类似 TikTok 的 category_report）或**相似产品/详情查询**来进行。让 Agent 运行的时候，如果发现没有直接叫 _search 的接口，允许它自动使用该平台的 **similar_product****（相似产品）** 或 **product_detail****（产品详情）** 接口来获取同款的“月销、价格、星级、评论数”，这样完全不影响你的逻辑，且符合 [Sorftime MCP](https://seller.sorftime.com/mcp?atag=MjAxODA5MTMyMzIwMzU1NzAwMDE~) 的底层设计。"}],"timestamp":1780473111559}}
