{"type":"message","id":"4c8bb25b","parentId":"b79526ed","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:53:03.703Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to update the Feishu doc as well. The doc is at https://www.feishu.cn/docx/KlpcdGesGoIii9xPEZYcMa3znNd (doc_id: KlpcdGesGoIii9xPEZYcMa3znNd).\n\nI need to update the Phase 2 section to reflect the change from shopee_product_search to shopee_similar_product with fallback to shopee_product_request.\n\nI'll use feishu_update_doc to make this change. The text to find is the old version of the Phase 2 section.","thinkingSignature":"9dd3b44fe46c195bfbd429af705a81011c7a7c143346532913412e2e5c90c810"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNow update the Feishu doc. I'll use update_doc to replace the Phase 2 section:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0efb7b7b2e4240829e0f7213","name":"feishu_update_doc","arguments":{"doc_id":"KlpcdGesGoIii9xPEZYcMa3znNd","markdown":"### 阶段2：Shopee平台生命周期验证\n**每日额度≤200次**\n\n- 对阶段1输出的商品，调用 `shopee_similar_product`（越南+泰国站点）用标题关键词搜索同款\n- 备用方案：如 similar_product 未返回有效数据，自动调用 `shopee_product_request`（需productId）\n- 验证标准（100%基于Sorftime可返回字段）：\n  - 必过：同款月销≥500单、商品评分≥4.2、近7天评论数正增长\n  - 加分：同款竞品≤5个、Shopee平均售价高于TikTok售价15%以上\n  - 拦截：无同款、退货率≥12%、评分<4.0、评论中出现\"易断\"\"掉色\"\"质量差\"关键词≥3次\n\n- 输出：Shopee月销、评分、竞品数量、平均价格、差评关键词","mode":"replace_all","selection_with_ellipsis":"### 阶段2：Shopee平台生命周期验证...输出：Shopee月销、评分、竞品数量、平均价格、差评关键词"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":360,"output":439,"cacheRead":114752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115551,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780473177064,"responseId":"066f10595815bd60875f00cb22ed0174"}}
