{"type":"message","id":"b3268711","parentId":"14f52ae1","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:53:12.516Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the Feishu doc has been updated. Now let me also update the MEMORY.md to note that the SOP v6.0 has been updated with the shopee_similar_product suggestion.\n\nAlso, I should let the user know what was done.","thinkingSignature":"454373e7d36de0e92f73096523197050ed08e9c4b97a758d242da8177fe0b078"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n已同步。更新汇总：\n\n**✅ 本地文件** `/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v6.0.md`\n- 阶段2：改用 `shopee_similar_product` + 备用 `shopee_product_request`\n\n**✅ 飞书文档** `https://www.feishu.cn/docx/KlpcdGesGoIii9xPEZYcMa3znNd`\n- 同步更新了阶段2的接口描述\n\n**变更内容：**\n\n| 原描述 | 更新后 |\n|--------|--------|\n| 批量调用 `shopee_product_search` | 调用 `shopee_similar_product` 用标题关键词搜索同款 |\n| — | 新增：备用方案 `shopee_product_request` |\n\n---\n\n这样 agent 在执行阶段2时会更灵活——优先用关键词搜相似款，找不到再用 productId 查详情，不会因为接口不匹配就卡住。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":561,"output":244,"cacheRead":115072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115877,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780473186861,"responseId":"066f10643b108cba4948b6e25f52a8ea"}}
