{"type":"message","id":"a3956c97","parentId":"6c8d3604","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:54:10.999Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to run the selection workflow once now (手动跑一次). This is a one-time execution of the v6.0 SOP to test it out.\n\nLet me execute the workflow:\n1. Phase 1: Call tiktok_similar_product to find hair accessories trending on TikTok (Vietnam + Thailand sites)\n2. Filter by the criteria: 24h sales growth ≥100%, video count ≥8, rating ≥4.2, price $1.5-$8\n3. Phase 2: For products that pass, call shopee_similar_product to verify\n4. Phase 3: For products that pass phase 2, call ali1688_similar_product for supply chain/profit calculation\n\n\n5. Write results to the Feishu bitable\n\nNow I'll start by calling the tiktok_similar_product API with hair clip keywords to surface trending products in the Vietnam market.","thinkingSignature":"46d1e2a5c3f87806dd2bb4fa442a5a596ac93f205d9c51d8776a6ea07512bdb6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，手动跑一轮 v6.0 选品流程。\n\n**阶段1：TikTok 发饰黑马抓取**\n\n先用 TikTok 搜索越南+泰国站点的发饰产品：\n\n**越南站点（VN）：**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_eba81d68fc9044dabb393dbd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call \"sorftime-mcp.tiktok_similar_product(searchName: \\\"hair clips\\\", site: \\\"VN\\\", page: 1)\" --config /home/halei/workspace-tts/config/mcporter.json 2>&1 | head -60"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1393,"output":310,"cacheRead":114496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116199,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780473243959,"responseId":"066f109c68a93ff823e32986c999a6d1"}}
