{"type":"message","id":"70f24ad0","parentId":"e2622d53","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:54:28.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I'm getting Vietnamese language results from TikTok Vietnam. The prices are in Vietnamese Dong (VND), not USD. I need to convert them.\n\nLet me check the price criteria: $1.5-$8 USD\n\n16999 VND = about $0.68 USD\n37536 VND = about $1.50 USD\n5355 VND = about $0.21 USD\n17000 VND = about $0.68 USD\n29000 VND = about $1.16 USD\n\nActually, let me look at the actual prices. The prices are showing in what looks like VND (Vietnamese Dong):\n- 16999 VND ≈ $0.68 USD - too low\n- 37536 VND ≈ $1.50 USD - at the minimum\n- 5355 VND ≈ $0.21 USD - too low\n\n\n- 17000 VND ≈ $0.68 USD - too low\n- 29000 VND ≈ $1.16 USD - too low\n\nThe higher price points seem to be:\n- 29000 VND ≈ $1.16 USD - still below $1.5\n\nI'm realizing I need to recalculate this properly. Using the exchange rate of approximately 1 USD ≈ 24,000 VND, I can convert these values more accurately. The issue is that even the highest price I found (29000 VND) converts to only about $1.21, which falls short of the $1.5 minimum threshold.\n\nLooking back at the results, I should verify I'm looking at actual hair clips rather than other hair accessories. I also need to account for the fact that TikTok Shop displays prices in local currency (VND for Vietnam, THB for Thailand), and the search is being done with the \"VN\" site parameter but I'm seeing results with \"my\" IDC codes, which suggests the data might be coming from Malaysia instead.\n\nThe most straightforward approach is to filter for prices between 10000-50000 VND (roughly $0.42-$2.08 USD), then look at products with weekly sales of at least 100 units and ratings of 4.2 or higher. Let me also search the Thailand site to get a better sense of the actual product range.\n\nFor Thailand, prices are in THB, so I'm looking at a $1.5-$8 range which translates to roughly 50-280 THB. Let me pull the Thailand data with similar filters and then run both searches in parallel to see what products actually meet these criteria.","thinkingSignature":"285aa33b454b6d243ad56710e733d40baaba037fdacd99b8116400f7823f29f3"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好的，正在跑。先搜索泰国站点，同时整理越南站点数据：\n\n**泰国站点（TH）：**\n\n| ProductId | 标题 | 周销量 | 月销量 | 价格(VND) | 星级 | 评论数 |\n|-----------|------|--------|--------|-----------|------|--------|\n| 1734141996809291509 | Kẹp Tết Tóc Mái 3 Tầng (三层发夹) | 7109 | 49609 | 16,999₫ | 4.6 | 14090 |\n| 1731984802588690363 | Kẹp Tóc Lì Đơn Giản (简单马尾夹) | 3579 | 22254 | 37,536₫ | 4.4 | 992 |\n| 1732201409050150421 | 10 Miếng dán tóc đen (10片黑发贴) | 2899 | 10671 | 5,355₫ | 4.5 | 10012 |\n| 1731908439623042569 | KẹP TóC ĐU ĐưA (摇摆发夹) | 1124 | 6431 | 17,000₫ | 4.6 | 1877 |\n| 1731119475382716903 | Băng Đô Cài Tóc Thỏ (兔子头箍+发夹) | 1354 | 5853 | 29,000₫ | 4.7 | 587 |\n\n越南价格是越南盾（VND），需要换算：1 USD ≈ 24,500 VND\n\n让我也搜一下泰国站点：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_79d3b17294d740e09a7b1ff6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter call \"sorftime-mcp.tiktok_similar_product(searchName: \\\"hair clips\\\", site: \\\"TH\\\", page: 1)\" --config /home/halei/workspace-tts/config/mcporter.json 2>&1 | head -60"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1662,"output":954,"cacheRead":115840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118456,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780473256240,"responseId":"066f10a8e4bec049a9bef5d84e1f3d14"}}
