{"type":"message","id":"5ec38fc7","parentId":"39f38f62","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:55:02.644Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The TH (Thailand) site returned an error. Let me try with a different approach - maybe the site code is different. Looking at the tool definition, the sites are: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\". \n\nWait, Thailand is not in the list! The tiktok_similar_product tool supports: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\". Thailand (TH) is not a valid site option.\n\nThis is a problem. The SOP says to monitor Vietnam + Thailand sites, but the tiktok_similar_product tool doesn't support Thailand (TH) site. The available sites are:\n- US\n- MY (Malaysia)\n- PH (Philippines)  \n- VN (Vietnam)\n- ID (Indonesia)\n- GB (United Kingdom)\n\nSo Thailand is not available! I need to note this limitation and adjust. Maybe I should use the Thailand site code differently, or use the \"my\" (Malaysia) site as a proxy for Thailand, or just focus on Vietnam since that's the primary market anyway.\n\nLet me also try tiktok_product_trend to see if that has different site support.\n\nActually, looking at the tool definition again:\n```\nfunction tiktok_similar_product(searchName: string, page?: number, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n```\n\nThailand (TH) is not in the list. And looking at tiktok_product_trend:\n```\nfunction tiktok_product_trend(productId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\");\n```\n\nThailand is also not available for tiktok_product_trend. So the Thailand market data might not be accessible through these APIs.\n\nI should focus on what's available:\n- Vietnam (VN) is available ✓\n- Thailand (TH) is NOT available ✗\n\nThis is a significant limitation of the current tool setup. I need to inform the user that Thailand site is not supported in the current Sorftime MCP configuration, and adjust the strategy accordingly.\n\nFor now, I'll work with Vietnam data and note this limitation. Let me proceed with the analysis of the Vietnam data I already have. The prices are in VND, so I'll convert them: 16999 VND ≈ $0.69, 37536 VND ≈ $1.53, 5355 VND ≈ $0.22, 17000 VND ≈ $0.69, 29000 VND ≈ $1.18.\n\nMost products fall below the $1.5 minimum price threshold, but the second product (37536 VND / ~$1.53) just barely meets it. The others are too cheap to qualify.\n\nLooking at the actual products themselves, the top result is a tiered hair clip set with 49,609 monthly sales and a 4.6 rating—it's performing exceptionally well. The second product is a simple hairpin with 22,254 monthly sales and a 4.4 rating. The third appears to be a black hair patch or extension product.\n\nThe challenge is that most items fall below the $1.5 price minimum, so I need to examine the data more carefully to find products that actually meet the criteria. I should try searching with different keywords to surface items in the right price range.","thinkingSignature":"b7c59c08fa1afd82e60f3d8a6ef318ea4b1bb580465505f0892981775fd645c7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThailand 站点不在支持列表里。工具支持：`US | MY | PH | VN | ID | GB`（没有 Thailand）。这是工具限制。\n\n越南站点数据我有了，现在按 v6.0 标准筛选：\n\n**价格换算**：1 USD ≈ 24,500 VND\n\n| 标题 | 价格(VND) | ≈ USD | 周销量 | 月销量 | 星级 | 评论数 | 通过？ |\n|------|----------|-------|--------|--------|------|--------|--------|\n| 三层发夹 | 16,999₫ | $0.69 | 7109 | 49609 | 4.6 | 14090 | ❌ 价格太低 |\n| 简单马尾夹 | 37,536₫ | $1.53 | 3579 | 22254 | 4.4 | 992 | ✅ 刚好过 |\n| 10片黑发贴 | 5,355₫ | $0.22 | 2899 | 10671 | 4.5 | 10012 | ❌ 价格太低 |\n| 摇摆发夹 | 17,000₫ | $0.69 | 1124 | 6431 | 4.6 | 1877 | ❌ 价格太低 |\n| 兔子头箍+发夹 | 29,000₫ | $1.18 | 1354 | 5853 | 4.7 | 587 | ❌ 价格太低 |\n\n只有\"简单马尾夹\"勉强过 $1.5 门槛。但问题是 TikTok 的价格是越南盾，转化后大部分品在 $0.2-$1.5 之间——越南市场的发饰价格带偏低。\n\n**新发现：SOP 里的 $1.5-$8 门槛可能需要调整**——越南发饰爆款的实际价格集中在 $0.5-$2 这个区间。\n\n让我用不同关键词再搜一轮越南站，看能不能找到更高单价的发饰品：\n\n**第二轮搜索（更精准的关键词）：**\n\n`hair claw clips` 在越南：\n\n`hair claw` 在越南：\n\n`mái tóc` (发型) 在越南：\n\n`kẹp tóc` 是发夹的越南语关键词。让我用越南语关键词搜：\n\n---\n\n越南市场发饰价格偏低，可能是因为：\n1. 越南消费者偏好低价走量\n2. TikTok 越南站点定价用越南盾，$1.5 相当于 ~36,750 VND，门槛偏高\n\n**建议调整越南市场的价格门槛为 $0.8-$5**，和泰国/马来西亚拉开差距。\n\n让我先完成这轮测试，把\"简单马尾夹\"推进阶段2验证：\n\n**阶段2：Shopee 越南验证**\n\n用标题关键词搜索同款：\n\n`kẹp tóc lì đơn giản` 在 Shopee 越南站点验证：\n\n`kẹp tóc lì` 简单发夹\n\n`kẹp tóc` 发夹\n\n`hair pin` 发夹\n\nLet me also try searching with different keywords and then do the Shopee verification on the product that passed Phase 1.\n\nThe main issue I'm seeing is that the Vietnam market has very low price points for hair accessories. The $1.5-$8 USD threshold in the SOP is too high for this market. I should note this and suggest an adjustment to the SOP for Vietnam specifically.\n\nLet me run a broader search to get more product candidates, then do the Phase 2 verification on the top candidates.\n</think>\n\n等等——发现一个问题。越南盾价格换算后大部分品低于 $1.5 门槛。让我多搜几个关键词找更多候选，再统一筛选：\n\n**用更多关键词扫描越南 TikTok：**\n\n`claw clip`、`hair pin`、`tóc`、`hair accessory`：\n\n`claw clip` 越南：\n\n`hair pin` 越南：\n\n`accessory tóc` 越南：\n\nLet me do a broader search to get a better sample, then process everything together.\n\nActually, the user said \"跑一次\" (run once). Let me be more efficient. Let me:\n1. Search with multiple keywords in parallel\n2. Aggregate all results\n3. Filter by criteria\n4. Run Phase 2 on the best candidates\n5. Run Phase 3\n6. Write to bitable\n\nLet me execute all the searches at once:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0a8ac9588f2a4b35ba1f9a9a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Search with multiple keywords for Vietnam site\nmcporter call \"sorftime-mcp.tiktok_similar_product(searchName: \\\"claw clip\\\", site: \\\"VN\\\", page: 1)\" --config /home/halei/workspace-tts/config/mcporter.json > /tmp/vn_claw.json 2>&1 &\nmcporter call \"sorftime-mcp.tiktok_similar_product(searchName: \\\"hair pin women\\\", site: \\\"VN\\\", page: 1)\" --config /home/halei/workspace-tts/config/mcporter.json > /tmp/vn_pin.json 2>&1