{"type":"message","id":"355264bb","parentId":"623bf378","timestamp":"2026-06-03T07:55:22.602Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, all searches are done. Now let me process all the data and filter by the v6.0 criteria. Let me parse all the files and extract the products that meet the criteria.\n\nKey criteria for Phase 1:\n- 24h sales growth ≥100% (I don't have this directly - I have weekly and monthly sales)\n- Video count ≥8 (need to check if tiktok_similar_product returns this)\n- Rating ≥4.2\n- Price $1.5-$8 (need to convert VND to USD)\n- No IP issues (no branded/cartoon characters)\n\nThe tiktok_similar_product returns: ProductId, 主图, Title, 品牌, 周销量, 月销量, 价格, 卖家, 星级, 评论数量\n\nIt doesn't seem to return video count or 24h sales growth. This is a limitation of the tool. I'll need to:\n1. Use weekly/monthly sales as a proxy for growth\n2. Skip the video count requirement if the tool doesn't provide it\n\nLet me parse the data and see what we have.\n\nThe prices are in VND (Vietnamese Dong). 1 USD ≈ 24,500 VND.\n\n$1.5 = ~36,750 VND\n$8 = ~196,000 VND\n\nLet me filter by:\n- Price between 36,750 and 196,000 VND\n- Rating ≥ 4.2\n- Monthly sales ≥ some threshold\n\nLet me process all the data.","thinkingSignature":"cd66d63245cdc598268d2ebfdeb2a048bfbc06bd2bc1af699fbe4dd3141b6fce"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNow let me process all the data and filter by v6.0 criteria:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_52eb61b00b654697ae38bd50","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'PYEOF'\nimport json\nimport os\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# Exchange rate VND to USD\nVND_TO_USD = 1 / 24500\n\nfiles = {\n    'claw clip': '/tmp/vn_claw.json',\n    'hair pin': '/tmp/vn_pin.json', \n    'hair band': '/tmp/vn_band.json',\n    'headband': '/tmp/vn_headband.json',\n    'hair ties': '/tmp/vn_ties.json'\n}\n\nall_products = []\n\nfor keyword, filepath in files.items():\n    try:\n        with open(filepath) as f:\n            content = f.read().strip()\n            if content.startswith('['):\n                products = json.loads(content)\n            else:\n                # Each line might be a JSON object\n                products = []\n                for line in content.split('\\n'):\n                    line = line.strip()\n                    if line and not line.startswith('[') and not line.startswith(']') and not line.startswith(','):\n                        try:\n                            products.append(json.loads(line))\n                        except:\n                            pass\n        for p in products:\n            p['搜索词'] = keyword\n            all_products.append(p)\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"Error reading {filepath}: {e}\")\n\nprint(f\"Total products collected: {len(all_products)}\")\n\n# Filter by v6.0 criteria\n# Price: $1.5-$8 USD = 36,750 - 196,000 VND\n# Rating: ≥4.2\n# Monthly sales: some threshold (let me use >500 as baseline for TikTok virality)\n# Brand: not Generic? Actually Generic is fine for hair accessories\n\nVND_MIN = 36750  # $1.5\nVND_MAX = 196000  # $8\n\nfiltered = []\nfor p in all_products:\n    try:\n        price = float(p.get('价格', 0))\n        rating = float(p.get('星级', 0))\n        monthly = int(p.get('月销量', 0) or 0)\n        weekly = int(p.get('周销量', 0) or 0)\n        reviews = int(p.get('评论数量', 0) or 0)\n        \n        if price < VND_MIN or price > VND_MAX:\n            continue\n        if rating < 4.2:\n            continue\n        if monthly < 500:\n            continue\n            \n        filtered.append({\n            'productId': p.get('ProductId'),\n            'title': p.get('标题', ''),\n            'brand': p.get('品牌', 'Generic'),\n            'price_vnd': price,\n            'price_usd': round(price * VND_TO_USD, 2),\n            'weekly': weekly,\n            'monthly': monthly,\n            'rating': rating,\n            'reviews': reviews,\n            'seller': p.get('卖家', ''),\n            'image': p.get('主图', ''),\n            'keyword': p.get('搜索词', ''),\n            'growth_ratio': round(weekly * 4 / monthly, 2) if monthly > 0 else 0  # Approximate weekly/monthly ratio\n        })\n    except Exception as e:\n        pass\n\nprint(f\"\\n通过价格($1.5-$8)+星级≥4.2+月销≥500筛选: {len(filtered)} 个\")\n\n# Sort by monthly sales descending\nfiltered.sort(key=lambda x: x['monthly'], reverse=True)\n\nprint(\"\\n=== Phase 1 通过商品（按月销排序）===\")\nfor i, p in enumerate(filtered[:15]):\n    print(f\"\\n{i+1}. {p['title'][:50]}\")\n    print(f\"   ProductId: {p['productId']}\")\n    print(f\"   价格: {p['price_vnd']:,.0f}₫ (${p['price_usd']}) | 周销: {p['weekly']} | 月销: {p['monthly']} | 星级: {p['rating']} | 评论: {p['reviews']}\")\n    print(f\"   搜索词: {p['keyword']} | 卖家: {p['seller']}\")\n\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1378,"output":1234,"cacheRead":119168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121780,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780473309112,"responseId":"066f10dda2ed44b689168d7ff63d8f1e"}}
