ent approach.\n\nActually, looking at the error more carefully - \"NOTEXIST\" could mean:\n1. The app_token is wrong (but it was working before)\n2. The bitable doesn't exist\n3. The bot doesn't have permission\n\nLet me try to list the bitable records to see if the connection works:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e31658537bc54f4fa2a79749","name":"feishu_bitable_app_table_record","arguments":{"action":"list","app_token":"***","page_size":3,"table_id":"tblHU2do30jzinJT"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":689,"output":587,"cacheRead":128000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129276,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780473404491,"responseId":"066f113c36c7b7510255c262bb7e68fe"}}
