{"type":"message","id":"b8814ed1","parentId":"7b885680","timestamp":"2026-06-03T08:03:08.254Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still NOTEXIST. Let me think about this. The list works but create/update don't. This is strange.\n\nWait - maybe the issue is that I'm using the wrong authentication context. The feishu_bitable tools use \"以用户身份\" (user identity). But maybe the user OAuth token is not properly set up for write operations?\n\nLet me check if there's a way to debug this. Actually, let me try using the feishu_oauth tool to check if there are any auth issues, or try a different approach.\n\nActually, let me look at this from a different angle. The user said the bot has edit permissions. The list works, so the app_token is correct. But create/update fail with NOTEXIST.\n \nThis could mean the user identity context is missing write permissions even if the bot itself has edit rights, or there's something wrong with the specific table or record format. Let me check if the field names match what's actually defined in the table - I see things like \"三级类目\", \"产品连接\", \"售价（本地货币）\", \"增长率\", \"月销量\", \"利润率\" - but maybe one of these doesn't exist in the table schema.\n\nLooking at the field definitions, I notice \"预估利润\" instead of \"估利润\" - that's likely the issue. Let me also verify the \"1688产品主图\" field type since it's an attachment field and might need special formatting. The \"IP风险\" field is a SingleSelect so that should accept string values like \"无\" without issues.","thinkingSignature":"b45840635f0fdc9703fa2bd357758c4f294afb6442a19e53d8e652a59b3ecbc3"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n单条写入也失败。让我检查一下字段名是否匹配。字段名\"估利润\"可能是错的，应该是\"预估利润\"：\n\n| 字段 | 我的值 | 实际字段名 |\n|------|--------|-----------|\n| 1688价格(CNY) | ✅ | ✅ |\n| 预估利润 | ❌ \"估利润\" | ✅ \"预估利润\" |\n| 站点 | ❌ \"单\" | ✅ \"站点\" |\n\n让我用正确的字段名重试：\n\n| 等级 | 商品 | TikTok月销 | 售价 | 1688采购价 | 毛利估算 |\n|------|------|-----------|------|-----------|---------|\n| **S级** | 发带(dây buộc tóc) | 25,902 | $1.84 | ¥0.78 | ~51% |\n\n---\n\napp_token = `AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd`\ntable_id = `tblHU2do30jzinJT`\n\n正确字段名重试：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_198b81e5b00a430a8d4ebded","name":"feishu_bitable_app_table_record","arguments":{"action":"create","app_token":"***","fields":{"1688价格(CNY)":0.78,"1688同款链接":"https://detail.1688.com/offer/904476900797.html","三级类目":"发圈","售价（本地货币）":1.84,"增长率":1,"月销量":25902,"利润率(%)":51,"站点":"越南","预估利润":0.94,"推荐等级":"S","采集状态":"已采集","IP风险":"无","行动建议":"立即采购首选50-100件","选品来源":["Sorftime-TK数据"]},"table_id":"tblHU2do30jzinJT"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2696,"output":737,"cacheRead":129280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132713,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780473776696,"responseId":"066f12b1b9270195b5a50ad08ee837ea"}}
