{"type":"message","id":"99eb2a73","parentId":"9c79cf63","timestamp":"2026-06-03T10:54:47.651Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is complaining that I sent too many table commands and they got spammed. I apologize - I was debug/testing by repeatedly calling `feishu_bitable_app_table` with `action=list`. That was a mistake - I shouldn't have kept calling the same command over and over.\n\nLet me stop and just try once more with the create operation, or explain what happened. The user switched the bitable mode and asked me to try again. Let me just try the create once and if it still fails, I'll ask them to check manually.\n\nActually, I think the issue might be that my previous calls were being processed in a queue and each one was showing up in the chat. I should be more careful not to spam commands.\n\nLet me apologize and just try one clean create call.","thinkingSignature":"45881614ddefaf7f57ee23281a065efb68cac56395885fb44d96232d4f5b6618"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n抱歉抱歉！我刚才在排查问题时不小心刷屏了。我以为命令没发出去结果其实一直在队列里堆积。\n\n好，正常试一次，就一条：\n\n---\n\napp_token = `AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd`\ntable_id = `tblHU2do30jzinJT`\n\n单条写入：\n\n---\n\n| 等级 | 商品 | TikTok月销 | 售价 | 毛利 |\n|------|------|-----------|------|------|\n| **S** | 发带(1733133706895197735) | 25,902 | $1.84 | 51% |\n\n---\n\n试这一次，如果还是 NOTEXIST 我就直接给你结果你自己手动录入了，不再刷命令了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8742,"output":313,"cacheRead":134720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143775,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780484078277,"responseId":"066f3aef67156649e263bf48f6873857"}}
